-Methods
  A class consists of variables and methods
  -Can a class have just the variables - Yes
  -Can a class have only the methods ?

  -Methods: Action performed over the variables of the class.
          : Everytime you wish to perform some action and in order to do so you need the help of variables of the class- You have to create method

  Syntax:
        accessModifier[public/private] returnType[void/dataTypes] methodName(can/t parameters)
        {
            Action over the class variables
        }

  ------------------------------------------------------------
  Make Tea: [Method]
   -Milk Powder
   -Sugar
   -Tea Leaves
   -Water
